3.20	Belluton	Belluton	Belluton is a village in Somerset, England. It is in the district of Bath and North East Somerset and is located due south of the city of Bristol and due west of the city of Bath. The eastern end of the village is defined by the A37 road.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e0/Belluton_Travellers_Rest.jpg/240px-Belluton_Travellers_Rest.jpg
